GetFutureSaltsRequest R6 class

GetFutureSaltsRequest.Rd

Represents the TL request `GetFutureSaltsRequest`.

R6 class representing a request to get future salts. Contains methods for serialization to list and bytes.

Details

Fields: - num: integer (32-bit)

Methods: - new(num): create new instance. - to_list(): return an R list representation. - to_raw(): serialize to raw vector (bytes) in little endian as used in TL.

Writes constructor id 0xb921bd04 as little-endian bytes: 0x04 0xBD 0x21 0xB9, then writes num as 4-byte little-endian integer.
